\u00e6rt gjennom en evaluering f\u00f8r han sier at de ikke har det, sier Blekesaune til Under Dusken.", "F\u00f8rsteamanuensisen p\u00e5peker at sosiologistudiet ved NTNU siden 2009 har v\u00e6rt med i den tilsvarende evalueringen som biologistudiet har v\u00e6rt gjennom."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "student"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "de574f8b43a0bd719fb0edd0eb57922c314af425a60f2337cdab022485124a16"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-05-24T13:42:55.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Det er ikke planlagt endringer i sosiologistudet etter Hjernevask-debatten i v\u00e5r. N\u00e5 kritiserer NTNU-institutter hverandre."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1365714.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/gl%C3%B8s"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/d6817adff8c417a70199a27c9c7fe8a3620bc186.jpg?596f2f3e"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Dumt, ubegrunnet og usaklig -adressa.no", "Uro i milj\u00f8et", "Kritiserer sosiologene", "Sl\u00e5r tilbake"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "d6817adff8c417a70199a27c9c7fe8a3620bc186"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "student"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["debatt", "saken", "studiet", "sosiologi", "institutt", "sosiologer", "endre", "kritiserer sosiologene", "planlagt endringer"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["under dusken", "hjernevask", "institutt"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["harald eias", "eivind r\u00f8sk